Virgin Money in Talks to Buy Norwich & Peterborough, Times Says

-- B y   L i n d s a y   F o r t a d o
-- 
2011-03-06T13:24:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-06/virgin-money-in-talks-to-buy-norwich-peterborough-times-says.html
  Richard Branson ’s financial services
business, Virgin Money Holdings UK Ltd., is in talks to buy
Norwich & Peterborough Building Society, the Sunday Times
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The Peterborough, England-based Norwich & Peterborough is
one of Britain’s largest building societies with 500,000 members
and 45 branches, the newspaper said.  Virgin Money spokesman Scott Mowbray declined to comment on
the report. “As we’ve always said, we are interested in growing
our business and will look at relevant opportunities that
present themselves,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lindsay Fortado in London at 
